{"tid":2149073,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"多個傳媒組織聯署對警搜查記者物品表震驚　促警方交代","createTime":"2020-08-10T08:25:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T16:24:44.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e8b663cb8772a84ce7261b8e280d29b6e6225053","tid":2149073,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:25:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542863-20200810.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542863-20200810.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mGXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=ff1f7bd2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542863-20200810.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e5cc40e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542863-20200810.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n香港記者協會等多個傳媒工會及組織，發表聯署聲明，對警方拘捕壹傳媒創辦人黎智英等人，先後到其寓所及壹傳媒大樓蒐證，有警務人員搜查記者座位內的個人物品，表示震驚。<br />\n<br />\n他們批評警方搜查新聞材料，將引起寒蟬效應，令知情人士不敢向傳媒揭露黑幕，削弱傳媒的監察功用，嚴重踐踏新聞自由，要求警方盡快交代搜查目的及法律理據，否則應立即停止搜查。<br />\n<br />\n聯署信亦對警方一度拒絕部分媒體進入採訪區，並解釋現場不寬敞，只能容納少量傳媒進內，故揀選一些本地、規模較大、過往警方行動中沒對警方帶來阻礙和威脅的傳媒入內，表示強烈不滿，指出警察公共關係科的做法與篩選傳媒無異，嚴重踐踏新聞自由。<br />\n<br />\n參與聯署的包括香港記者協會、香港攝影記者協會、獨立評論人協會、大專新聞教育工作者聯席、眾新聞工會、明報職工協會、壹傳媒工會和香港電台節目製作人員工會。"},{"pid":"2bea9e689e636c5ca4bbfb907261c068661bbb9c","tid":2149073,"uid":14494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:28:19.000Z","msg":"一係你就收晒番去嚇鳩人<br />\n純粹行過手多揭2頁jm9擺明比位人入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44197b01ab38c889ab47724bf6aaf67b96e1e04b","tid":2149073,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T09:01:58.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9086abaa8f87062b941829e0f89b0f4eae0e8879","tid":2149073,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T16:24:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b51aadcd10d97ee110a3c12020ade4d70ba379","tid":2149073,"uid":38533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T16:24:44.000Z","msg":"衰多手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}